FBIS3-53959 "drnes014_l_94003" FBIS-NES-94-014 Document Type:Daily Report 21 Jan 1994 ISRAEL Rabin Aide Reveals Referendum 8 Months in Planning TA2001160694 Jerusalem Qol Yisra'el in Hebrew 1400 GMT 20 Jan 94 TA2001160694 Jerusalem Qol Yisra'el Language: Hebrew Article Type:BFN [Text] Shim'on Sheves, the director general of the Prime Minister's Office, revealed that a team under his supervision had begun examining the possibility of holding a national referendum eight months ago. Sheves dismissed all the reports claiming that the proposal had been made on the spur of the moment.
